title: Ivanka Trump: Dad disrupting 2016 race in 'positive way'
text: Photo: Carolyn Kaster, AP Ivanka Trump, daughter of Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump, founder and CEO, Ivanka Trump Collection and executive vice president Development and Acquisitions The Trump Organization, speaks at the Fortune Most Powerful Women Summit, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015, in Washington. Ivanka Trump, daughter of Republican presidential candidate Donald... WASHINGTON (AP) — Ivanka Trump says she's "incredibly proud" of her dad for running for president. But she's more ambivalent about whether she's happy about it.
